'''中國中獸屬'''（[[學名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Sinonyx''}}，意為「中國的爪」）是一類像[[狼|狼]]的[[中爪獸科|中爪獸科]][[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]，生存於5600萬年前[[古新世|古新世]]晚期的[[中國|中國]]。牠們是中爪獸科的早期原始形態。中國中獸是由[[密西根大學|密西根大學]]的[[菲利浦·金格里奇|菲利浦·金格里奇]]（Philip Gingerich）在中國[[安徽|安徽]]發現。

中國中獸約有5呎長，頭部較長及大，腳短，趾上有細小的蹄。牠有持久力及強壯，能獵食行動緩慢的獵物及沿海岸吃腐肉。牠共有44顆[[牙齒|牙齒]]，是原始哺乳動物的齒數，且與現今哺乳動物[[異型齒|異型齒]]不同。其[[臼齒|臼齒]]是非常窄的切齒，但有多個齒冠。大的頭顱骨有特長的[[枕骨|枕骨]]及大的[[矢狀嵴|矢狀嵴]]，但[[腦部|腦部]]細小。大的矢狀嵴可以連接強壯的[[下頜骨|下頜骨]][[肌肉|肌肉]]，顯示牠有咬勁。<ref name=Nesbit>{{cite journal en | author = Nesbit, Joanne | year = 2001 | title = Medical Illustrator Makes Puzzle Pieces Fit | journal = The University Record Online, University of Michigan | issue = March 25, 1997 | pages = 1019-1027 | url = http://www.umich.edu/~urecord/9697/Mar25_97/artcl01.htm | access-date = 2008-04-08 | archive-date = 2007-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070605032838/http://www.umich.edu/~urecord/9697/Mar25_97/artcl01.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==與鯨魚相同之處==
[[科學家|科學家]]一直認為中國中獸就是[[鯨目|鯨目]]的直系祖先，但[[古鯨亞科|古鯨亞科]]的發現及[[DNA|DNA]]與[[分子|分子]]研究都顯示鯨目是較接近[[河馬|河馬]]及其他[[偶蹄目|偶蹄目]]。<ref name=Geisler>{{cite journal en | author = Geisler, J.H. and Uhen, M.D. | year = 2003 | title = Morphological support for a close relationship between hippos and whales | journal = Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology | volume = 23 | pages = 991-996}}</ref><ref name=Geisler2>{{cite journal en | author = Geisler, J.H. and Uhen, M.D. | year = 2005 | title = Phylogenetic relationships of extinct cetartiodactyls: results of simultaneous analyses of molecular, morphological, and stratigraphic data | journal = Journal of Mammalian Evolution | volume = 12 | issue = 1 and 2 | pages = 145-160}}</ref><ref name=Boisserie>{{cite journal en | author = Boisserie, J.−R., Lihoreau, F., and Brunet, M. | year = 2005 | title = The position of Hippopotamidae within Cetartiodactyla | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences | volume = 102 | pages = 1537-1541}}</ref><ref name=Gatesy>{{cite journal en | author = Gatesy, J., Hayashi, C., Cronin, A., and Arctander, P. | year = 1996 | title = Evidence from milk casein genes that cetaceans are close relatives of hippopotamid artiodactyls | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-biology-and-evolution_1996-09_13_7/page/954 | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | volume = 13 | pages = 954-963}}</ref>

中國中獸特長的鼻端及[[牙齒|牙齒]]形狀在[[中爪獸目|中爪獸目]]中是非典型的，而是較接近鯨目，在原始的[[鯨魚|鯨魚]]中都有這類特徵。特長的鼻端往往都是用來獵食[[魚類|魚類]]，可見中國中獸正發長出後來鯨魚般生活模式的適應性。[[三角形|三角形]]的牙齒上有明顯的齒冠，而每邊的齒冠都是相同大小的，這點亦很像鯨目。其他相似的地方包括沒有[[鎖骨|鎖骨]]及專門的上肢骨、特大的[[頸靜脈孔|頸靜脈孔]]及較短的頭蓋骨基部。<ref name=Zhou>{{cite journal en| author = Zhou X., Zhai R., Gingerich P. and L. Chen | year = 1995 | title = Skull of a new Mesonychid (Mammalia, Mesonychia) from the late Paleocene of China | journal = Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology | volume = 15 | issue = 2 | pages = 387-400}}</ref>另外，中爪獸目是唯一[[肉食性|肉食性]]的[[有蹄動物|有蹄動物]]，雖然鯨目有濾食性動物，但沒有鯨目是[[植食性|植食性]]的。再者，原始[[胎盤|胎盤]]動物有[[軟骨|軟骨]]的[[鼓泡|鼓泡]]，並有薄及環形的[[鼓骨|鼓骨]]來支撐[[鼓膜|鼓膜]]，但中國中獸的整個鼓泡像鯨魚般已經僵化。較厚的報泡及較密的鼓骨可以更有效的抵抗壓力，阻隔[[聲音|聲音]]至頭顱骨的其他部份，並能提高聲音的[[頻率|頻率]]。<ref name=Carrol>{{cite book en | author = Carrol, Robert Lynn | year = 1997 | title = Patterns and Processes of Vertebrate Evolution | journal = Palaeontology | publisher = Cambridge University Press | pages = 464 pages | id = ISBN 052147809X}}</ref>

